    <string name="help3">First, choose your faction and race.</string>

    <string name="help4">You can test your Warcraft knowledge by playing Easy, Medium or Hard tier.\n\nEach tier contains ten, randomly generated, questions. Depending on your score, you can be awarded with Bronze, Silver or Golden medal.</string>

